{"tid":41692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解mario run 唔用課金制 用買斷制","createTime":"2016-12-16T05:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T04:04:03.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a395facf1bad2208e9321248c56bf42cfa93e3bb","tid":41692,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔肯畀錢嘅用咩制都唔會畀錢 但係買斷制就會放棄咗呢班人 呢班人雖然唔可以直接帶來收入 但係可以帶動到更加多人玩 最少個熱潮唔會咁快完先<br />\n肯畀錢玩嘅可以玩得好癲 課金買道具幾萬蚊都可以照買<br />\n但係買斷制偏偏局限咗呢樣嘢 俾一舊錢就可以玩到全部內容  咁樣收入唔係仲少咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00859c76e013fb470ddddc63599706b64f2cf6b5","tid":41692,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"唔好玩<br />\n<br />\n唔會買<br />\n<br />\nGame已del"},{"pid":"5c0b60ae1c7026cca86ee61464a6e888f7620116","tid":41692,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"佢遲下實出課金道具架啦你放心都得啦"},{"pid":"b85383ba451faf71290220992ccf5f4bdf06d32b","tid":41692,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢遲下實出課金道具架啦你放心都得啦</blockquote><br />\n隻game有咩道具可以出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個玩法太容易   隻game難玩都可能會引到啲人買道具"},{"pid":"fbdbe554dd8ea8129ceed9b038dde4654ce65c31","tid":41692,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418b37e2e3b0a38afa88d02ee32b2c01c0fc3d1f","tid":41692,"uid":47523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"dlc=冇熱潮<br />\n商城=搵笨<br />\n<br />\n利申，裝都廢時，因為真係唔好玩"},{"pid":"d6e87812f72d92511c96713450008cc0bada5b00","tid":41692,"uid":6137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢遲下實出課金道具架啦你放心都得啦</blockquote><br />\n隻game有咩道具可以出<img src=\"/asse