應該可以換衫之類 咁就可以開課金 完全諗唔明老任呢個係咩策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢就係唔想玩課金制做壞Mario個名"},{"pid":"1c94a42df3374ae55099ad3ea5211b8ffce310f9","tid":41692,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就算買關都應該唔好一次過買曬6關<br />\n應該分開6關咁買 同埋mario 應該可以換衫之類 咁就可以開課金 完全諗唔明老任呢個係咩策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢就係唔想玩課金制做壞Mario個名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解課金就係做壞名？有咩衝突"},{"pid":"de6d24a83d462d24dfee759ee91ba2f16b897bb8","tid":41692,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"隻Game其實關卡設計真心高質<br />\n你見啲遊戲評測網全部都俾佢高分就知<br />\n同埋每一關唔同色既coins個關卡設計都會有少少唔同 其實幾襟玩<br />\n但真係衰在佢頭三關俾唔到俾左最簡單嗰幾關人玩<br />\n俾唔到人值78蚊既感覺"},{"pid":"7f59635887b654614717fac298c9c193d683ec6d","tid":41692,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就算買關都應該唔好一次過買曬6關<br />\n應該分開6關咁買 同埋mario 應該可以換衫之類 咁就可以開課金 完全諗唔明老任呢個係咩策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢就係唔想玩課金制做壞Mario個名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解課金就係做壞名？有咩衝突</blockquote><br />\nFor Nintendo, premium is out of the question. Iwata says that premium games are generally not doing well, and it remains to be seen if the likes of Square Enix agrees or not. The price of premium games are sometimes prohibitively expensive, going as high as $20. On the other hand, <span style=\"color: red;\">Nintendo doesn&rsquo;t want to be associated with the free-to-play games that are notorious for either their lack of quality or their obvious attempts to milk players out of their money</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.slashgear.com/nintendo-to-aim-for-a-free-to-start-mobile-gaming-model-06391767/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slashgear.com%2Fnintendo-to-aim-for-a-free-to-start-mobile-gaming-model-06391767%2F&d=jFRzrmQ0gnZ14QXzMB2KFnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7eebc8e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.slashgear.com/nintendo-to-aim-for-a-free-to-start-mobile-gaming-model-06391767/</a>"},{"pid":"0ac97e6146fee43787d19fda8776d34707d983ab","tid":41692,"uid":1972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"日本大廠 有企業良心掛 唔想你地課到破產"},{"pid":"01eb4f417edebbd6ec9fd0fc8badd47826b2999f","tid":41692,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本大廠 有企業良心掛 唔想你地課到破產</blockquote><br />\n寶可夢..."}]}